title: Tammy and the Doctor [1963 - USA] (Sandra Dee) romance comedy
description:
Tammy and the Doctor (1963 - USA)

Comedy / Romance

starring . . . . Sandra Dee, Peter Fonda, Macdonald Carey, Adam West
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0057558/


Southern sweetheart Tammy Tyree takes her search for love to Los Angeles. A matronly friend of hers requires heart surgery, and so naturally Tammy goes along as moral support. To cover her expenses, the effervescent girl takes a job at the local hospital as a nurse's assistant. Before long, she becomes smitten with hunky physician Dr. Mark Cheswick.
